  stimulus_text = 'The author of the novel *The Adventures of Huckleberry Finn*  is Mark Twain. The story follows the experiences of Huckleberry Finn, a young boy who runs away from home and travels down the Mississippi River with an escaped slave. Twain''s novel is widely considered to be a classic of American literature. It has been praised for its realism, its humor, and its social commentary.',
